{"tid":2515812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月25號，向喺亂港暴動中受害嘅市民獻花，有冇得諗","createTime":"2021-05-04T08:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T08:46:18.000Z","uid":370061,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"782ed26e8d7c22e085efdfd3fc6734ee66dcb463","tid":2515812,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oSV7ZnZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoSV7ZnZ.jpg&h=17d1d672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林彬（1929年9月24日－1967年8月25日），原名林少波，香港播音員。林彬於1960年代擔任香港商業電台播音員。1967年，香港表面親中共和左派人士、實際為香港地下黨的黨員們，為了響應文化大革命，在香港展開六七暴動行動。由於林彬在電台節目中抨擊有關人士的暴力行為，於同年8月24日在九龍何文田窩打老道山嘉鳴閣對開馬路上被伏擊，其人連同座駕遭到縱火，燒至重傷，翌日不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n死暴徒，點解要搞亂香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324e27c8576525e941c475f1601564eed6a85593","tid":2515812,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"我只係熱愛香港，向<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">反暴力而受害的</span></span>香港市民獻花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5d3cd5b0960b278d49c6a9697e8485f8692ff0","tid":2515812,"uid":32722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"324e27c8576525e941c475f1601564eed6a85593","tid":2515812,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:43:07.000Z","msg":"我只係熱愛香港，向<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">反暴力而受害的</span></span>香港市民獻花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:44:50.000Z","msg":"一見你係連登仔發起, 一律拉去還柙半年<br />\n理得你係咪合法"},{"pid":"0f0876e11389b528d059c6f0dbdbe9b60b14651e","tid":2515812,"uid":373921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"林x波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj